'''2016年麥克默里堡森林大火'''發生於2016年5月1日，起火點位於[[加拿大|加拿大]][[艾伯塔|艾伯塔]]省[[麦克默里堡|麦克默里堡]]西南方15公里外的偏遠地區<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://edition.cnn.com/2016/05/09/americas/fort-mcmurray-fire-canada/ |title = Fort McMurray fire: 2,400 structures gone, 10% of city destroyed |author = Holly Yan, Dan Simon |date = 2016-05-09 |publisher = CNN |accessdate = 2016-05-10 |archive-date = 2016-05-10 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160510110503/http://www.edition.cnn.com/2016/05/09/americas/fort-mcmurray-fire-canada/ |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=145001 |title = 「野獸」肆虐！原油年產量砍半　加拿大大火還要燒數月 |author = 鍾宇皓 |date = 2016-05-09 |publisher = 三立新聞網 |accessdate = 2016-05-10 |archive-date = 2016-05-10 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160510112600/http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=145001 |dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |last=Edwards |first=Peter |url=https://www.thestar.com/news/canada/2016/05/05/more-communities-evacuated-as-fort-mcmurray-fire-moves-south.html |title=Fire evacuees north of Fort McMurray to be airlifted out as 1,100 firefighters battle inferno |publisher=Toronto Star |date=2016-05-05 |accessdate=2016-05-10 |archive-date=2019-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190419224304/https://www.thestar.com/news/canada/2016/05/05/more-communities-evacuated-as-fort-mcmurray-fire-moves-south.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Convoys May 6" />。5月3日，大火蔓延至麦克默里堡，燒毀超過2400棟住家及建築，並觸發艾伯塔史上最大規模的居民撤退行動<ref name="largestAB"/>。大火在亞省北部蔓延，並於5月19日進入[[薩克其萬省|薩克其萬省]]<ref name="EJ160520">{{cite news |author1=Parsons, Paige |author2=Gerein, Keith |url=http://edmontonjournal.com/news/local-news/fort-mcmurray-fire-crosses-into-saskatchewan-and-continues-to-grow |title=Fort McMurray evacuees to receive 'welcome packages' as they return home |newspaper=''Edmonton Journal'' |date=2016-05-20 |accessdate=2016-05-20 |archive-date=2016-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160519154803/http://edmontonjournal.com/news/local-news/fort-mcmurray-fire-crosses-into-saskatchewan-and-continues-to-grow |dead-url=no }}</ref>，最終燃燒近{{convert|590000|ha|acre}}土地；當局於7月5日宣佈火勢受控<ref name="CBC160705">{{cite web |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/fort-mcmurray-wildfire-now-considered-under-control-1.3664947 |title=Fort McMurray wildfire now considered under control |publisher=CBC News |date=2016-07-05 |accessdate=2016-07-05 |archive-date=2016-07-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160708010213/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/fort-mcmurray-wildfire-now-considered-under-control-1.3664947 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

這場林火影響加拿大的油砂業運作<ref name="SyncrudeShutdown">{{cite news|last1=Jones|first1=Jeffrey|title=Syncrude Canada oil sands operation shut down, staff removed, due to Fort McMurray fire|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/report-on-business/industry-news/energy-and-resources/syncrude-canada-oil-sands-shut-down-staff-removed-due-to-fire/article29932912/|date=2016-05-07|accessdate=2016-05-07|work=The Globe and Mail|archive-date=2016-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160510222822/http://www.theglobeandmail.com/report-on-business/industry-news/energy-and-resources/syncrude-canada-oil-sands-shut-down-staff-removed-due-to-fire/article29932912/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並為加拿大史上經濟損失最大的災難<ref name="Insurance estimates"/><ref name="CTV160707"/>。

== 天氣狀況 ==
2015年至2016年冬季亞省北部較正常乾燥，地面積雪較過去冬季為少並迅速融化，當地樹林因此缺乏水分<ref>{{cite news|last1=McGrath|first1=Matt|title='Perfect storm' of El Niño and warming boosted Alberta fires|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-36212145|accessdate=2016-05-07|work=[[BBC_News|BBC News]]|agency=[[BBC|BBC]]|date=2016-05-05|archive-date=2019-04-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190419224522/https://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-36212145|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=ClimateCentral>{{cite news|last1=Kahn|first1=Brian|title=Here’s the Climate Context For the Fort McMurray Wildfire|url=http://www.climatecentral.org/news/climate-context-fort-mcmurray-wildfire-20311|accessdate=2016-05-07|work=Climate Central|date=2016-05-04|archive-date=2019-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190511125654/https://www.climatecentral.org/news/climate-context-fort-mcmurray-wildfire-20311|dead-url=no}}</ref>。踏入2016年5月初，一股異常地酷熱和乾燥的空氣集結在亞省北部，為麥克默里堡一帶帶來破紀錄高溫。該帶氣溫於5月3日升至{{convert|32.8|C|0}}<ref name="Fort McMurray CS">{{cite web |url=http://climate.weather.gc.ca/climateData/dailydata_e.html?timeframe=2&Prov=AB&StationID=27216&dlyRange=1996-05-01%7C2016-05-03&Year=2016&Month=5&Day=1 |title=Daily Data Report for May 2016 |accessdate=2016-05-06 |publisher=[[加拿大環境部|加拿大環境部]] |date=2016-05-06 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20160506153357/http://climate.weather.gc.ca/climateData/dailydata_e.html?timeframe=2&Prov=AB&StationID=27216&dlyRange=1996-05-01%7C2016-05-03&Year=2016&Month=5&Day=1 |archive-date=2016-05-06 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，[[相對濕度|相對濕度]]則低至12%<ref name="3 May 2016">{{cite web|url=http://climate.weather.gc.ca/climateData/hourlydata_e.html?timeframe=1&Prov=AB&StationID=27216&dlyRange=1996-05-01%7C2016-05-03&Year=2016&Month=5&Day=3|title=Hourly Data Report for May 03, 2016|accessdate=2016-05-06|publisher=[[加拿大環境部|加拿大環境部]]|date=2016-05-06|archive-date=2020-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200404194525/http://climate.weather.gc.ca/climateData/hourlydata_e.html?timeframe=1&Prov=AB&StationID=27216&dlyRange=1996-05-01%7C2016-05-03&Year=2016&Month=5&Day=3|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。5月4日的氣溫達至{{convert|31.9|C|0}}<ref name="Fort McMurray CS"/>，陣風風速則達每小時{{convert|72|km|0}}<ref name="Fort McMurray A">{{cite web|url=http://climate.weather.gc.ca/climateData/dailydata_e.html?timeframe=2&Prov=AB&StationID=49490&dlyRange=2011-10-20%7C2016-05-04&Year=2016&Month=5&Day=1|title=Daily Data Report for May 2016|accessdate=2016-05-06|publisher=[[加拿大環境部|加拿大環境部]]|date=2016-05-06|archive-date=2020-04-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200404194527/http://climate.weather.gc.ca/climateData/dailydata_e.html?timeframe=2&Prov=AB&StationID=49490&dlyRange=2011-10-20%7C2016-05-04&Year=2016&Month=5&Day=1|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。乾涸的木林加上高溫，令火勢一發不可收拾<ref name="largestAB">{{cite news|last1=Parsons|first1=Paige|title=Thousands flee from Fort McMurray wildfire in the largest fire evacuation in Alberta's history|url=http://edmontonjournal.com/news/local-news/fort-mcmurray-wildfire-pushed-back-even-as-temperatures-climb|accessdate=2016-05-03|newspaper=Edmonton Journal|publisher=Postmedia Network|date=2016-05-03|archive-date=2016-05-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160510222635/http://edmontonjournal.com/news/local-news/fort-mcmurray-wildfire-pushed-back-even-as-temperatures-climb|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 災情進展 ==
[[File:2016_Fort_McMurray_wildfire_(1).jpg|thumb]]

麥克默里堡所屬的[[伍德布法羅地區自治市|伍德布法羅地區自治市]]於5月1日晚上9時57分（世界協調時5月2日03:57）頒佈地方緊急狀態，將百年拖車公園（{{lang|en|Centennial Trailer Park}}）以及草原溪（{{lang|en|Prairie Creek}}）和格雷戈瓦（{{lang|en|Gregoire}}）社區列為强制疏散範圍<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/fort-mcmurray-braces-for-high-winds-in-battle-with-wildfire-1.3562108 |title=Fort McMurray braces for high winds in battle with wildfire |last=Snowdon |first=William |date=2016-05-02 |work=CBC News Edmonton |accessdate=2016-05-03 |archive-date=2016-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160510223122/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/fort-mcmurray-braces-for-high-winds-in-battle-with-wildfire-1.3562108 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://edmontonjournal.com/news/local-news/fires-threatening-fort-mcmurray |title=Wildfire continues to threaten Fort McMurray neighbourhood |last1=McDermot |first1=Vincent |last2=French |first2=Janet |date=2016-05-02 |work=Edmonton Journal |accessdate=2016-05-03 |archive-date=2016-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160510223257/http://edmontonjournal.com/news/local-news/fires-threatening-fort-mcmurray |dead-url=no }}</ref>。隨著火勢改往西南方蔓延並離開該帶，當局於5月2日晚上將上述社區的强制疏散令降格為自願留守令<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.fortmcmurraytoday.com/2016/05/02/crews-resume-battling-wildfires-near-fort-mcmurray-no-change-since-last-night |title='A great day for us': Wildfire moves away from Fort McMurray as crews fight blaze |last1=McDermot |first1=Vincent |last2=Bird |first2=Cullen |date=2016-05-02 |newspaper=Fort McMurray Today |accessdate=2016-05-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160503121030/http://www.fortmcmurraytoday.com/2016/05/02/crews-resume-battling-wildfires-near-fort-mcmurray-no-change-since-last-night |archive-date=2016-05-03 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://globalnews.ca/news/2673945/residents-on-alert-as-three-wildfires-burn-near-fort-mcmurray/ |title='We are in for a rough day': Fort McMurray wildfire expected to flare up Tuesday afternoon |last1=Ivanov |first1=Jennifer |last2=Bartko |first2=Karen |last3=Heidenreich |first3=Phil |date=2016-05-03 |work=Global News |accessdate=2016-05-04 |archive-date=2016-05-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160503205359/http://globalnews.ca/news/2673945/residents-on-alert-as-three-wildfires-burn-near-fort-mcmurray/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

然而隨著火勢增强，當局於5月3日下午5時（世界協調時23:00）恢復强制疏散令，覆蓋範圍擴展至該帶12個社區<ref name="FMCCBC">{{cite web|title=Wildfire destroys Fort McMurray homes, most of city evacuated|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/fort-mcmurray-fire-social-media-reflects-fear-worry-as-the-flames-enter-city-1.3564982|accessdate=2016-05-03|work=CBC News Edmonton|date=2016-05-03|archive-date=2019-02-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190214175252/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/fort-mcmurray-fire-social-media-reflects-fear-worry-as-the-flames-enter-city-1.3564982|dead-url=no}}</ref>，再於下午6時49分（世界協調時5月4日00:49）擴展至麥克默里堡全境<ref name="largestAB" /><ref name="alberta">{{cite web|url=http://wildfire.alberta.ca/wildfire-status/wildfire-status-map.aspx|title=Wildfire Status Map | ESRD - Wildfire|publisher=wildfire.alberta.ca|accessdate=2016-05-06|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160505193915/http://wildfire.alberta.ca/wildfire-status/wildfire-status-map.aspx|archivedate=2016-05-05}}</ref>。當局再於5月4日晚上9時50分（世界協調時5月5日03:50）將鄰近的安扎克（{{lang|en|Anzac}}）、格雷戈瓦湖莊園（{{lang|en|Gregoire Lake Estates}}）和麥克默里堡原住民保留區（{{lang|en|Fort McMurray First Nation}}）納入强制疏散範圍<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.rmwb.ca/News-Room/Media-Releases/Municipality-Announces-Mandatory-Evacuations-for-Anzac--Gregoire-Lake-Estates-and-Fort-McMurray-First-Nation_s2_p5451.htm | title=Municipality Announces Mandatory Evacuations for Anzac, Gregoire Lake Estates and Fort McMurray First Nation | publisher=Regional Municipality of Wood Buffalo | date=2016-05-04 | accessdate=2016-05-05 | archive-date=2018-11-16 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181116045750/http://www.rmwb.ca/News-Room/Media-Releases/Municipality-Announces-Mandatory-Evacuations-for-Anzac--Gregoire-Lake-Estates-and-Fort-McMurray-First-Nation_s2_p5451.htm | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。約8萬8千名居民從麥克默里堡一帶疏散，無人直接因火災受傷或死亡<ref name="No hurt tweet"/>，但兩人則在疏散期間遇上車禍喪生<ref name="Traffic deaths"/>。

伍德布法羅地區自治市官員於5月4日公佈麥克默里堡内的燈塔山（{{lang|en|Beacon Hill}}）、阿巴桑德（{{lang|en|Abasand}}）和沃特韋斯（{{lang|en|Waterways}}）社區受到嚴重破壞<ref name="Wood Buffalo Update">{{cite web | url=http://asset.rmwb.ca/wildfire/ | title=Fort McMurray Wildfire Updates | publisher=Regional Municipality of Wood Buffalo | date=2016-05-04 | accessdate=2016-05-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160505193825/http://asset.rmwb.ca/wildfire/ | archive-date=2016-05-05 | dead-url=yes }}</ref>。[[阿爾伯塔省省長|亞省省長]][[瑞秋·諾特利|諾特利]]在當日早上記者會中公佈麥克默里堡内逾1600座建築物焚毀，單在燈塔山社區便有近600座民居付諸一炬<ref name="GlobalMay4AMupdate">{{cite news |last=Barkto |first=Karen |url=http://globalnews.ca/news/2679178/fort-mcmurray-wildfire-how-many-homes-have-been-lost-in-the-fire/ |title=Fort McMurray wildfire update: Roughly 1600 buildings destroyed in 'catastrophic' fire |publisher=Global News |date=2016-05-04 |accessdate=2016-05-04 |archive-date=2019-04-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190424183753/https://globalnews.ca/news/2679178/fort-mcmurray-wildfire-how-many-homes-have-been-lost-in-the-fire/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。當局又估計已有約{{convert|10,000|ha|acre}}土地被焚<ref name="North fly out">{{cite news |last=Edwards |first=Peter |url=https://www.thestar.com/news/canada/2016/05/05/more-communities-evacuated-as-fort-mcmurray-fire-moves-south.html |title=ire evacuees north of Fort McMurray to be airlifted out as 1,100 firefighters battle inferno |publisher=Toronto Star |date=2016-05-05 |accessdate=2016-05-05 |archive-date=2019-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190419224304/https://www.thestar.com/news/canada/2016/05/05/more-communities-evacuated-as-fort-mcmurray-fire-moves-south.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。由於火勢仍未受控，當局呼籲沿亞伯達63號公路北行方向撤退至麥克默里堡以北地域的居民留在原位，不要沿該公路南行方向折返<ref name="Wood Buffalo Update" />；當局又於5月4日向麥克默里堡全境頒佈煮沸食水指示<ref name="GlobalMay4AMupdate" />。[[麥克默里堡國際機場|麥克默里堡國際機場]]於5月4日日間中止商營民航服務，而大火則於當日下午4時（世界協調時22:00）左右迫近機場<ref name="Wood Buffalo Update" /><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/catastrophic-fort-mcmurray-wildfire-prompts-state-of-emergency-1.3566310 |title='Catastrophic' Fort McMurray wildfire prompts state of emergency |last=McConnell |first=Rick |date=2016-05-04 |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2016-05-04 |quote= |archive-date=2016-05-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160505025117/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/catastrophic-fort-mcmurray-wildfire-prompts-state-of-emergency-1.3566310 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，迫使在機場旁設立的地區緊急運作中心遷至別處<ref name="spread south May 5">{{cite web |title=Fort McMurray evacuees flee again as fire spreads: 'It's almost like it's following us' |url=http://news.nationalpost.com/news/canada/fort-mcmurray-evacuees-flee-again-as-fire-spreads-its-almost-like-its-following-us |accessdate=2016-05-05 |work=National Post |date=2016-05-05 |archive-date=2016-05-07 |archive-url=https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20160507061711/http://news.nationalpost.com/news/canada/fort-mcmurray-evacuees-flee-again-as-fire-spreads-its-almost-like-its-following-us |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

