大火於5月5日繼續往南蔓延，覆蓋面積達至{{convert|85000|ha|acre}}<ref name="North fly out" /><ref name="spread south May 5" />。亞省政府於同日早上10時（世界協調時16:00）宣佈伍德布法羅地區自治市進入省級緊急狀態<ref name="AB update May 5">{{cite web |url=http://www.alberta.ca/release.cfm?xID=41701E7ECBE35-AD48-5793-1642C499FF0DE4CF |title=Update 2: Fort McMurray Wildfire (May 5 at 10 a.m.) |date=2016-05-05 |publisher=Government of Alberta |accessdate=2016-05-05 |archive-date=2019-05-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190512224856/https://www.alberta.ca/release.cfm?xID=41701E7ECBE35-AD48-5793-1642C499FF0DE4CF |dead-url=no }}</ref>。救災行動包括1千1百名工作人員、45部直升機、138件重型器材和22部空中滅火機<ref name="AB update May 5" />。

省政府於5月5日宣佈將2萬5千名疏散至麥克默里堡以北油砂工作營地的災民中約8千人經空路運送至首府[[愛民頓|愛民頓]]和該省最大城市[[卡加利|卡加利]]<ref name="BBC160506">{{cite news |title=Canada wildfire: Thousands airlifted from Fort McMurray as blaze grows |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-36218996 |accessdate=2016-05-07 |work=BBC News |date=2016-05-06 |archive-date=2016-05-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508104655/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-36218996 |dead-url=no }}</ref>；行動涉及[[皇家加拿大空軍|皇家加拿大空軍]]一部[[C-130運輸機|大力士運輸機]]以及當地油砂業者的飛機<ref name="North fly out" />。餘下滯留北部油砂工作營地的災民則從5月6日起分批經陸路撤退：在[[加拿大皇家騎警|加拿大皇家騎警]]帶領下，1500部汽車分成每組50部車，陸續沿63號公路南下愛民頓<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rcmp-grc.gc.ca/ab/news-nouvelles/2016/05/160506-wood-buffalo-fire-feux-2-eng.htm|title=RCMP to escort northern evacuees through and out of the City - Update 2|last=|first=|date=2016-05-06|website=Royal Canadian Mounted Police|publisher=|accessdate=2016-05-06|archive-date=2016-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507065521/http://www.rcmp-grc.gc.ca/ab/news-nouvelles/2016/05/160506-wood-buffalo-fire-feux-2-eng.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.nationalpost.com/news/canada/the-beast-is-still-up-wildfire-evacuees-stuck-north-of-fort-mcmurray-moving-south-in-massive-rcmp-convoy|title=No stopping, go south, and follow the RCMP: Massive convoy helps fire evacuees trapped north get through city|last=Thomson|first=Graham|date=2016-05-06|work=|publisher=Postmedia News|newspaper=National Post|accessdate=2016-05-06|via=|archive-date=2016-05-07|archive-url=https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20160507050258/http://news.nationalpost.com/news/canada/the-beast-is-still-up-wildfire-evacuees-stuck-north-of-fort-mcmurray-moving-south-in-massive-rcmp-convoy|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Convoys May 6">{{cite web |title=‘The beast is still up’: Wildfire evacuees stuck north of Fort McMurray moving south in massive RCMP convoy |url=http://news.nationalpost.com/news/canada/the-beast-is-still-up-wildfire-evacuees-stuck-north-of-fort-mcmurray-moving-south-in-massive-rcmp-convoy |accessdate=2016-05-06 |work=National Post |date=2016-05-06 |archive-date=2016-05-07 |archive-url=https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20160507050258/http://news.nationalpost.com/news/canada/the-beast-is-still-up-wildfire-evacuees-stuck-north-of-fort-mcmurray-moving-south-in-massive-rcmp-convoy |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

當局於5月6日表示大火覆蓋範圍增至{{convert|100000|ha|sqmi}}，但增長速度略為放緩<ref name="Growth to 100000">{{cite web |title=Fort McMurray wildfire continues to grow out of control |url=http://www.news1130.com/2016/05/06/fort-mcmurray-wildfire-continues-to-grow-out-of-control/ |accessdate=2016-05-06 |work=News 1130 |date=2016-05-06 |archive-date=2016-05-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507131819/http://www.news1130.com/2016/05/06/fort-mcmurray-wildfire-continues-to-grow-out-of-control/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Convoys May 6" />。然而到了5月7日，大火覆蓋範圍增至{{convert|156000|ha|sqmi}}，並預料到當晚可達至{{convert|200000|ha|sqmi}}<ref name="CBC160507">{{cite news|last1=McConnell|first1=Rick|title=Fort McMurray wildfire could reach Suncor oilsands site today|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/fort-mcmurray-wildfire-saturday-1.3571678|website=CBC News|accessdate=2016-05-07|archive-date=2019-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190506052346/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/fort-mcmurray-wildfire-saturday-1.3571678|dead-url=no}}</ref>。隨著大火往東北蔓延，離麥克默里堡以北{{convert|54|km|mi}}的麥凱堡（{{lang|en|Fort McKay}}）進入自願疏散令<ref name="Campandcommunity">{{cite news|last1=Stolte|first1=Elise|title=Fort McKay under voluntary evacuation order as wildfire size expected to double|url=http://edmontonjournal.com/news/local-news/fort-mcmurray-wildfire-tense-evacuees-wait-for-new-convoys-saturday|accessdate=2016-05-07|agency=Edmonton jornal|publisher=Postmedia Network Inc|date=2016-05-07|archive-date=2016-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507173444/http://edmontonjournal.com/news/local-news/fort-mcmurray-wildfire-tense-evacuees-wait-for-new-convoys-saturday|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Voluntary Evacuation">{{cite news|last1=Bird|first1=Cullen|title=Fort McKay under voluntary evacuation order as wildfire size expected to double|url=http://www.fortmcmurraytoday.com/2016/05/07/fort-mckay-under-voluntary-evacuation-order-as-wildfire-size-expected-to-double|accessdate=2016-05-07|agency=Fort McMurray Today|publisher=Postmedia Network|date=2016-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160508112130/http://www.fortmcmurraytoday.com/2016/05/07/fort-mckay-under-voluntary-evacuation-order-as-wildfire-size-expected-to-double|archive-date=2016-05-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

大火在往後一周繼續在亞省北部的森林蔓延，5月16日燒至麥凱堡以南的油砂工人營地，8千名工人需從當地撤退，當中一座設有665個床位的宿舍被焚毀<ref name="Camps burn May 16">{{cite news|title=Fort McMurray fire sweeps east through northern oilsands sites|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/fort-mcmurray-oilsands-sites-fire-1.3585921|accessdate=2016-05-17|publisher=CBC News|date=2016-05-17|archive-date=2019-04-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190409210801/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/fort-mcmurray-oilsands-sites-fire-1.3585921|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Reuters oilsand shut cost">{{cite news |url=http://ca.reuters.com/article/topNews/idCAKCN0Y71ZT?sp=true |title=Canadian wildfire shifts north, prolonging oil sands shutdown |date=2016-05-17 |publisher=Reuters Canada |accessdate=2016-05-17 |archive-date=2018-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181106150143/https://ca.reuters.com/article/topNews/idCAKCN0Y71ZT?sp=true |dead-url=no }}</ref>。雖然大火已遠離麥克默里堡，但當地空氣質素仍然欠佳，加上發生兩宗爆炸，阻礙災民重返家園<ref name="Town explosions May 16">{{cite news |title=Wildfire heads towards oil plants as explosions hit Fort McMurray sites |url=https://www.thestar.com/news/canada/2016/05/17/fort-mcmurray-wildfire-forces-oil-industry-workers-to-evacuate.html |accessdate=2016-05-17 |publisher=Toronto Star |date=2016-05-17 |archive-date=2018-08-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180831104109/https://www.thestar.com/news/canada/2016/05/17/fort-mcmurray-wildfire-forces-oil-industry-workers-to-evacuate.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。到5月19日，火場面積增至{{convert|505000|ha|acre}}並蔓延至隔鄰的[[薩克其萬省|薩克其萬省]]<ref name="EJ160520" /><ref>{{cite web |title=Canadian Wildland Fire Information System |url=http://cwfis.cfs.nrcan.gc.ca/interactive-map?zoom=9&lon=-902990.75370526&lat=931229.14058237&month=05&day=18&year=2016#wb-cont |accessdate=2016-05-19 |publisher=[[加拿大自然資源部|加拿大自然資源部]] |date=2016-05-18 |archive-date=2016-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160611140927/http://cwfis.cfs.nrcan.gc.ca/interactive-map?zoom=9&lon=-902990.75370526&lat=931229.14058237&month=05&day=18&year=2016#wb-cont |dead-url=no }}</ref>，預料大火需時數個月才可撲熄<ref name="extinguishmonths">{{cite news|title=Blaze will take months to extinguish, Alberta fire official says|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/blaze-will-take-months-to-extinguish-alberta-fire-official-says/article29933091/|accessdate=2016-05-08|agency=The Globe and Mail|publisher=The Globe and Mail Inc.|date=2016-05-07|quote='It's going to take quite a while for the wildfire fighters to actually get that under control, contain it, put it out,' Scott Long, executive provincial operations director for the Alberta Emergency Management Agency|archive-date=2017-06-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170606060103/https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/national/blaze-will-take-months-to-extinguish-alberta-fire-official-says/article29933091/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

隨著當地氣溫於6月中回落並出現降雨，火場蔓延速度有所減退，而當局亦於7月5日宣佈火勢受控<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/fort-mcmurray-wildfire-mostly-contained-1.3632949 |title=Fort McMurray fire largely contained thanks to rain, firefighters' efforts |first=Wallis |last=Snowdon |publisher=CBC News |date=2016-06-13 |accessdate=2016-06-13 |archive-date=2016-06-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160613211204/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/fort-mcmurray-wildfire-mostly-contained-1.3632949 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="CBC160705" />。

== 救災反應 ==
亞省政府宣佈伍德布法羅地區自治市進入省級緊急狀態，並正式向[[加拿大軍隊|加拿大軍隊]]尋求協助<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.ctvnews.ca/canada/fort-mcmurray-fire-state-of-emergency-declared-1.2887111 |title=Fort McMurray fire: State of emergency declared |last=Dehaas |first=Josh |date=2016-05-04 |publisher=CTV News |accessdate=2016-05-04 |quote= |archive-date=2016-05-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160505015529/http://www.ctvnews.ca/canada/fort-mcmurray-fire-state-of-emergency-declared-1.2887111 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=Military air assets preparing to head to Fort McMurray: source |url=http://ipolitics.ca/2016/05/04/military-air-assets-preparing-to-head-to-fort-mcmurray-source/ |accessdate=2016-05-04 |work=iPolitics |date=2016-05-05 |archive-date=2016-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160506174628/http://ipolitics.ca/2016/05/04/military-air-assets-preparing-to-head-to-fort-mcmurray-source/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。省政府與[[加拿大國防部|國防部]]於5月4日簽定諒解備忘錄，確定包括派遣直升機在内等軍方所提供的協助<ref name="largestAB" />。其後軍方一架[[C-130運輸機|大力士運輸機]]從安大略省[[特倫頓空軍基地|特倫頓空軍基地]]啓程前往災區，其他軍方直升機亦派遣至當地<ref name="CBCTrudeauResponse">{{cite news|last1=Mas|first1=Susana|title=Trudeau says Canadians are united around Fort McMurray as federal response gets underway|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/trudeau-government-responds-fort-mcmurray-wildfires-1.3565723|accessdate=2016-05-04|agency=CBC News|date=2016-05-04|archive-date=2016-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160504192150/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/trudeau-government-responds-fort-mcmurray-wildfires-1.3565723|dead-url=no}}</ref>。亞省政府亦向[[安大略省|安大略省]]政府尋求協助，獲後者提供100名消防員和19名管理人員<ref name="largestAB" />。國内其他省份亦提供幫助<ref name="CBCTrudeauResponse" />，包括從[[魁北克省|魁北克省]]借出的四部CL-415[[滅火飛機|空中滅火機]]<ref>{{cite news
|title=Four water bombers heading to Alberta
|url=http://ici.radio-canada.ca/regions/quebec/2016/05/05/001-avions-cl-415-renfort-alberta-feux-foret.shtml
|accessdate=2016-05-05
