|dead-url=no
}}</ref>。

[[美國|美國]]、[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]、[[俄羅斯|俄羅斯]]、[[台灣|台灣]]、[[澳洲|澳洲]]和[[以色列|以色列]]等地政府皆有意向加國提供救火支援，但[[加拿大總理|總理]][[賈斯汀·杜魯多|杜魯多]]則以國内其他省份的消防人員已前往火場增援為由而婉拒<ref>{{cite news|title=Russian offer to send water bombers to fight Fort McMurray fire in limbo|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/russia-water-bombers-alberta-wildfires-1.3572825|website=CBC|accessdate=2016-05-08|date=2016-05-08|archive-date=2016-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160509002008/http://www.cbc.ca/news/politics/russia-water-bombers-alberta-wildfires-1.3572825|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.nationalpost.com/news/canada/justin-trudeau-turns-down-russian-u-s-mexican-offers-to-help-fight-fort-mac-wildfire|title=Justin Trudeau turns down Russian, U.S., Mexican offers to help fight Fort Mac wildfire|work=National Post|date=2016-05-09|accessdate=2016-05-09|archive-date=2016-05-09|archive-url=https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20160509220214/http://news.nationalpost.com/news/canada/justin-trudeau-turns-down-russian-u-s-mexican-offers-to-help-fight-fort-mac-wildfire|dead-url=no}}</ref>。然而隨著大火於5月中進一步威脅當地的油砂工地，亞省山火管理單位決定從國内其他省份、美國和[[南非|南非]]等地輸入逾一千名消防員參與救災<ref name="CBC160524">{{cite news|title=Alberta rallies international help for Fort McMurray wildfires|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/alberta-rallies-international-help-for-fort-mcmurray-wildfires-1.3597807|website=CBC|accessdate=2016-06-02|date=2016-05-24|first=Marion|last=Warnica|archive-date=2016-06-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160601103432/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/alberta-rallies-international-help-for-fort-mcmurray-wildfires-1.3597807|dead-url=no}}</ref>；約280名來自南非的消防員於5月29日飛抵亞省<ref>{{cite news|title=South African firefighters arrive eager to help fight Fort McMurray wildfire|url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/fort-mcmurray-fire-south-africa-1.3605976|website=CBC|accessdate=2016-06-02|date=2016-05-29|author1=Ross, Andrea|author2=Lamoureux, Mack|archive-date=2016-06-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160602050744/http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/fort-mcmurray-fire-south-africa-1.3605976|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

亞省政府又於5月4日宣佈對[[加拿大紅十字會|加拿大紅十字會]]所收到的捐款作出等額捐贈（即民眾每捐款一元政府也将捐一元）<ref name="MatchRedCross">{{cite web|title=Alberta Government matching Red Cross donations for Fort McMurray|url=http://www.alberta.ca/release.cfm?xID=41703E9EE402E-957B-30FA-5FC5EBFF81EA78B9|website=Alberta.ca|publisher=Alberta Government|accessdate=2016-05-05|archive-date=2016-05-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160505193915/http://www.alberta.ca/release.cfm?xID=41703E9EE402E-957B-30FA-5FC5EBFF81EA78B9|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而[[加拿大聯邦政府架構|加拿大联邦政府]]亦於5月5日作出相同承諾<ref name="North fly out" />。截至5月7日，紅十字會從國民收取的善款已達3千萬元<ref name="星島160507">{{cite news|title=一方有難各方支援數天已籌得逾3千萬 火場逾10萬頃 災民亟需救助|url=http://calgary.singtao.ca/282444/2016-05-07/post-%E4%B8%80%E6%96%B9%E6%9C%89%E9%9B%A3%E5%90%84%E6%96%B9%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4%E6%95%B8%E5%A4%A9%E5%B7%B2%E7%B1%8C%E5%BE%97%E9%80%BE3%E5%8D%83%E8%90%AC-%E7%81%AB%E5%A0%B4%E9%80%BE10%E8%90%AC%E9%A0%83/?variant=zh-hk|accessdate=2016-05-08|agency=《星島日報》卡加利版|date=2016-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160509101654/http://calgary.singtao.ca/282444/2016-05-07/post-%E4%B8%80%E6%96%B9%E6%9C%89%E9%9B%A3%E5%90%84%E6%96%B9%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4%E6%95%B8%E5%A4%A9%E5%B7%B2%E7%B1%8C%E5%BE%97%E9%80%BE3%E5%8D%83%E8%90%AC-%E7%81%AB%E5%A0%B4%E9%80%BE10%E8%90%AC%E9%A0%83/?variant=zh-hk|archive-date=2016-05-09|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。省府亦宣佈向災民發放緊急援助金，每名成人可獲1250元，每名少兒則可獲500元<ref>{{cite web|title=Here's our list of resources for Fort McMurray wildfire evacuees and how you can help|url=http://edmontonjournal.com/news/local-news/how-yiou-can-help-the-evacuees-from-the-fort-mcmurray-wildfires|website=Edmonton Journal|accessdate=2016-05-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160507221623/http://edmontonjournal.com/news/local-news/how-yiou-can-help-the-evacuees-from-the-fort-mcmurray-wildfires|archivedate=2016-05-07|language=en-US|date=2016-05-07|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="星島160507b">{{cite news|title=亞省派錢救急 每人發1,250元|url=http://vancouver.singtao.ca/558465/2016-05-07/post-%E4%BA%9E%E7%9C%81%E6%B4%BE%E9%8C%A2%E6%95%91%E6%80%A5-%E6%AF%8F%E4%BA%BA%E7%99%BC1250%E5%85%83/?variant=zh-hk|accessdate=2016-05-08|agency=《星島日報》溫哥華版|date=2016-05-07|archive-date=2016-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160509101123/http://vancouver.singtao.ca/558465/2016-05-07/post-%E4%BA%9E%E7%9C%81%E6%B4%BE%E9%8C%A2%E6%95%91%E6%80%A5-%E6%AF%8F%E4%BA%BA%E7%99%BC1250%E5%85%83/?variant=zh-hk|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

