=== 社區及基礎建設 ===
當局於5月4日初步估計麥克默里堡境内約有1600座建築物焚毀<ref name="GlobalMay4AMupdate"/>；省長諾特利於5月9日更新燒毀建築物數目至2400座，但麥克默里堡境内約85-90%建築則保存下來<ref name=CBCstillalive>{{cite news |last=McConnell |first=Rick |title=Fort McMurray is 'still alive,' fire chief says — but safety concerns linger |date=2016-05-09 |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/fort-mcmurray-tour-notley-media-1.3572982 |website=CBC News |access-date=2016-05-10 |archive-date=2019-05-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190503153535/https://www.cbc.ca/news/canada/edmonton/fort-mcmurray-tour-notley-media-1.3572982 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。當局於5月18日公佈已評估麥克默里堡境内19244座建築，當中1921座被燒毀、17156座可供民眾使用、121座可供有限度使用、39座因安全理由繼續封閉、另外7座則有待檢驗<ref name="GovARe-entry">{{cite web|title=Phased re-entry into Fort McMurray expected to start June 1|url=http://www.alberta.ca/release.cfm?xID=41776B85DAE7F-C0F6-C84E-6D5B0D3C26C65211|publisher=Government of Alberta|date=2016-05-18|accessdate=2016-05-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160521010210/http://www.alberta.ca/release.cfm?xID=41776B85DAE7F-C0F6-C84E-6D5B0D3C26C65211|archivedate=2016-05-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。截至5月24日，麥克默里堡全境約90%已恢復電力供應，而除了燈塔山、阿巴桑德和沃特韋斯三個重災區外，麥克默里堡其餘社區約99%戶已恢復天然氣供應<ref name="CBC160524"/>。[[麥克默里堡國際機場|麥克默里堡國際機場]]則於6月10日重啓商營民航服務<ref>{{cite news |last=Jellett |first=Stephanie |title=Fort McMurray Airport welcomes home first wave of passengers |date=2016-06-10 |url=http://www.fortmcmurraytoday.com/2016/06/10/fort-mcmurray-airport-welcomes-home-first-wave-of-passengers |website=''Fort McMurray Today'' |accessdate=2016-06-11 |archive-date=2016-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160611134833/http://www.fortmcmurraytoday.com/2016/06/10/fort-mcmurray-airport-welcomes-home-first-wave-of-passengers |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

亞省政府於5月18日宣佈從6月1日起分階段有條件允許從麥克默里堡疏散的災民重返家園<ref name="GovARe-entry"/>；截至6月8日早上有約42000名居民返回當地<ref>{{cite news |last=McDermott |first=Vincent |title=Painful homecoming for residents returning to worst-hit areas |date=2016-06-08 |url=http://www.fortmcmurraytoday.com/2016/06/08/painful-homecoming-as-residents-return-to-worst-hit-areas |website=''Fort McMurray Today'' |accessdate=2016-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160610140418/http://www.fortmcmurraytoday.com/2016/06/08/painful-homecoming-as-residents-return-to-worst-hit-areas |archive-date=2016-06-10 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

=== 油砂業運作 ===
麥克默里堡周邊的亞省東北部地區為加拿大的油砂業重鎮，這場大火嚴重影響當地產業。加拿大[[蜆殼公司|蜆殼公司]]位於麥克默里堡以北約70公里的艾比安油砂（{{lang|en|Albian Sands}}）中止採油運作；該公司提供降落跑道讓員工和家屬經空路撤離至愛民頓和卡加利，並提供兩支團隊支援當地的救火工作<ref name="Oilsands scaledown">{{cite news |url=http://www.montrealgazette.com/business/wildfire+forces+shell+canada+shut+down+oilsands+mining+project/11895999/story.html |title=Wildfire forces heart of Canada's oilsands to scale back production |date=2016-05-03 |publisher=Montreal Gazette |accessdate=2016-05-05 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160505140434/http://www.montrealgazette.com/business/wildfire+forces+shell+canada+shut+down+oilsands+mining+project/11895999/story.html |archivedate=2016-05-05 }}</ref>。至5月10日，艾比安油砂已恢復有限度運作<ref name="星島160511">{{cite news|title=油企與省長開會 部分油井陸續復產 林火加劇省財政壓力|url=http://calgary.singtao.ca/285470/2016-05-11/post-%e6%b2%b9%e4%bc%81%e8%88%87%e7%9c%81%e9%95%b7%e9%96%8b%e6%9c%83-%e9%83%a8%e5%88%86%e6%b2%b9%e4%ba%95%e9%99%b8%e7%ba%8c%e5%be%a9%e7%94%a2-%e6%9e%97%e7%81%ab%e5%8a%a0%e5%8a%87-%e7%9c%81%e8%b2%a1/?variant=zh-hk|accessdate=2016-05-11|newspaper=《星島日報》卡加利版|author=郭康立|date=2016-05-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160513031142/http://calgary.singtao.ca/285470/2016-05-11/post-%e6%b2%b9%e4%bc%81%e8%88%87%e7%9c%81%e9%95%b7%e9%96%8b%e6%9c%83-%e9%83%a8%e5%88%86%e6%b2%b9%e4%ba%95%e9%99%b8%e7%ba%8c%e5%be%a9%e7%94%a2-%e6%9e%97%e7%81%ab%e5%8a%a0%e5%8a%87-%e7%9c%81%e8%b2%a1/?variant=zh-hk|archive-date=2016-05-13|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。森科能源（{{lang|en|Suncor Energy}}）和Syncrude公司亦減產；兩間公司在其油砂工人營地安置約2千名災民<ref name="Oilsands scaledown" />。Syncrude於5月7日全面中止區内運作，並撤走4800名員工<ref name="SyncrudeShutdown" />。當地石油公司因這場大火每日減產約1百萬桶石油（即全國產油量的四分一）<ref name="SyncrudeShutdown" />。

=== 金融 ===
保險業初步估計重建整座城市的費用約90億[[加拿大元|加拿大元]]，將是加拿大史上損失最大的天災，超過{{link-en|1998年北美冰災|January 1998 North American ice storm}}（$19億）及[[2013年亞伯達洪水|2013年亞伯達洪水]]（$18億）。{{link-en|2011年奴湖森林大火|2011 Slave Lake wildfire}}則為加拿大史上損失最慘重的火災相關災害，破壞三分之一的奴湖村，造成7.5億加拿大元的損失。而此次森林大火造成損失預計達奴湖森林大火的10倍<ref name="Insurance estimates">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/business/fort-mcmurray-insurance-cost-1.3568113 |title=Fort McMurray fire could cost insurers $9B, BMO predicts |date=2016-05-05 |publisher=CBC News |accessdate=2016-05-05 |archive-date=2016-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160510222907/http://www.cbc.ca/news/business/fort-mcmurray-insurance-cost-1.3568113 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。保險業估計目前已發生損失約26億至47億加拿大元<ref>{{cite news |url=http://edmontonjournal.com/business/local-business/insurance-losses-from-fort-mcmurray-fire-could-top-9-billion-analyst-says |title=Insurance losses from Fort McMurray fire could top $9 billion, analyst says |date=2016-05-05 |publisher=''Edmonton Journal'' |accessdate=2016-05-05 |archive-date=2016-05-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160506172834/http://edmontonjournal.com/business/local-business/insurance-losses-from-fort-mcmurray-fire-could-top-9-billion-analyst-says |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而加拿大保險局則於7月7日表示這次林火造成損失約35億8千萬加元<ref name="CTV160707">{{cite news|last1=Romero|first1=Diego|title=Fort McMurray wildfires damage cost $3.58 billion|url=http://edmonton.ctvnews.ca/fort-mcmurray-wildfires-damage-cost-3-58-billion-1.2977275|accessdate=2016-07-07|work=CTV Edmonton|date=2016-07-07|archive-date=2018-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180720225215/https://edmonton.ctvnews.ca/fort-mcmurray-wildfires-damage-cost-3-58-billion-1.2977275|dead-url=no}}</ref>。<ref>{{Cite_news|author=小丶朱|title=大火过去六个月了 加拿大油砂产业又面临环保电影压力-市场观点-中金网|url=http://oil.cngold.com.cn/20161031d1820n96471219.html|accessdate=2016年11月15日|work=[[中金网|中金网]]|agency=中金网|date=2016年10月31日<!-- 17:23-->|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161116014918/http://oil.cngold.com.cn/20161031d1820n96471219.html|archive-date=2016年11月16日|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

